R3合併。<br />\n(Type1 Taste Receptor member 2 and 3)<br />\n<br />\n2.其後觸發一系列的細胞反應，並產生出鈣離子(Ca2+ ion)。<br />\n<br />\n3. 鈣離子觸動TRPM5，產生電流。<br />\n<br />\n4. 電流經由神經細胞傳到大腦。<br />\n<br />\n5. 大腦分析電流訊息，製造甜味的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）那麼，為何熱紅豆沙會比較甜呢？玄機就在圖中機制的第三步。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSONshN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSONshN.jpg&h=17a6bf5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTRPM5除了能夠感測鈣離子後，亦能感測溫度。<br />\n若然食物溫度提升的話，TRPM5所發出的電流強度便會有所增長。<br />\n而電流越強的話，大腦便會轉遞出越甜的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n而正正就是因為這個緣故，儘管糖份一樣，熱紅豆沙食起上來會比凍紅豆沙感覺起上來會比較甜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZtlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=545174fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZtlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=10553582\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。"},"citedB